    <item>
      <title>Instagram 和 Facebook 无广告，遭欧盟警告打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/meta-set-for-eu-warning-over-ad-free-instagram-facebook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 因其在 Instagram 和 Facebook 上采用的无广告服务订阅模式而受到警告，在欧盟根据严格的新规则对大型科技公司的最新打击中，该公司可能面临高额罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/meta-set-for-eu-warning-over-ad-free-instagram-facebook</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 08:33:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登盟友在周末疯狂竞选中拒绝辞职呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/biden-loyalists-dismiss-calls-to-quit-in-frenetic-weekend-blitz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在辩论中表现惨淡，遭到捐助者、顾问、官员和媒体的强烈反对，他们呼吁拜登退出 2024 年大选。拜登的竞选团队正在对此进行反击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/biden-loyalists-dismiss-calls-to-quit-in-frenetic-weekend-blitz</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 22:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普是总统还是普通公民：为什么最高法院的豁免裁决是一项考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/supreme-court-immunity-decision-could-save-trump-in-2020-election-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院将于周一就唐纳德·特朗普的说法作出裁决，特朗普称自己不会因试图推翻 2020 年大选结果而受到刑事指控，该案件很有可能被退回下级法院进行进一步的法律争论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/supreme-court-immunity-decision-could-save-trump-in-2020-election-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
